@startuml
actor Administrator as Admin
actor MaintenanceWorker as MW
participant MaintenancePlan as MP
participant MaintenanceTask as MT
participant Asset as Asset

Admin->>MP: 创建维护计划
activate MP
MP-->>Admin: 计划已生成
deactivate MP

MP->>MW: 分配巡检任务
activate MP
MW->>MT: 定期执行巡检计划
activate MT
MT->>Asset: 审查对应资产
activate Asset

alt 巡检正常
    Asset-->>MT: 状态正常
    MT->>MT: 记录正常
else 发现故障
    Asset-->>MT: 发现异常
    MT->>MT: 记录异常
    MT->>Asset: 送修
    Asset-->>MT: 更新送修状态
end

MT-->>MW: 结束
deactivate Asset
deactivate MT
MW->>MP: 报告任务完成
deactivate MP
@enduml